be enemies' weapons.<br>Turn on & off the lights, and you can sometimes destroy them.<br>Complete missions by using interactive objects such as controllable elevators and doors that open & close.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/998ac5e02eb988456a65543f50803b9c.poster.avif?t=1749785241\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/998ac5e02eb988456a65543f50803b9c.webm?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/998ac5e02eb988456a65543f50803b9c.mp4?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In-car navigation has a lot of information to help you play fake signals.<br>Information is about each stage, weapons, mails from the helper, soundtracks, bonus stages, etc.<br>Some apps can be unlocked by earning coins.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/a2f83209aa889c080905b9c8cbdbbb0c.poster.avif?t=1749785241\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/a2f83209aa889c080905b9c8cbdbbb0c.webm?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161430/extras/a2f83209aa889c080905b9c8cbdbbb0c.mp4?t=1749785241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
